Computer.file: The note, wow, never thought I'd write such thing... Time has passed and I've forgiven myself, but they, they helped me go through it, my friend wingy and... them...

The god, damn, last favor, never gonna use it again even though is not working... It's just a reminder that I shouldn't do that kind of stuff... Euthanasia is not the solution to your problems... You gotta be strong y'know? things may be hard but with time and effort, anything can be possible.

They freak me out, they always freaked me out, it's like they're always there waiting for something to happen, and if it doesn't happen they make it... I can't blieve such groups are allowed to even exist...
